<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>129</hymn_number>
<title>KALVARY CH129</title>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kalvary ah Jesuh a thi, A kan Khamhbawi khika'h an thah Keimah ca thi
 sung a chuak cang, Khi tlang in ngaihthiamnak a tling

[C1]
   Maw Kal-va-ry, Maw Kalvary, Khika'h kei ca a thi a chuak, Maw
   Kal-va-ry, Thluachuahnak tlang, Keimah Khamhtu thihnak a si.

[V2]
 Lungpi a kuai khua a mui dih, Khamhbawi a lu a khun, a thi Biaknak inn
 puan zar kha a tlek, Khamhnak lam tha kha a hun cang.

[C2]
   Maw Kal-va-ry, Maw Kalvary, Khika'h kei ca a thi a chuak, Maw
   Kal-va-ry, Thluachuahnak tlang, Keimah Khamhtu thihnak a si.

[V3]
 Maw Bawi Jesuh zeitin in dah, Vailam put in sifah na in, Kal-va-ry ah
 kei ca na thi, Na nunnak keimah ca na hloh.

[C3]
   Maw Kal-va-ry, Maw Kalvary, Khika'h kei ca a thi a chuak, Maw
   Kal-va-ry, Thluachuahnak tlang, Keimah Khamhtu thihnak a si.</lyrics>
</song>